    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute favorite ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been a total joy to own. Whether it's a quick trip to the store or a long weekend drive, this car has never let me down and still turns heads at every stoplight. She\u2019s got a few tiny 'character marks' here and there from some great adventures, but she\u2019s been loved and looked after like one of the family. The engine sounds sweet, the interior is super cozy, and she\u2019s just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. I\u2019d love for you to come by, have a chat, and see for yourself why I love this car so much!",
      "price": 31500.0,
