      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical purity: this unit features a high-revving, naturally aspirated heart with a powerband optimized for mid-range punch and high-end breathability. The 6-speed close-ratio transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagements with zero synchro grind, paired with a drivetrain that exhibits minimal lash. I've maintained strict adherence to fluid intervals, ensuring the internal rotating assembly remains within tight factory compression tolerances. The suspension geometry is dialed, providing exceptional tactile feedback through the rack while maintaining composure under heavy lateral loads. Recent service includes a comprehensive top-end inspection and a high-flow intake refresh to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. This is a stout, track-capable platform that has been babied in the garage and driven with precision.",
      "price": 38500.0,
